Titanic test data.

Titanic test data.

titanic_test

Format

Data frame with columns

PassengerId

Passenger ID

Pclass

Passenger Class

Name

Name

Sex

Sex

Age

Age

SibSp

Number of Siblings/Spouses Aboard

Parch

Number of Parents/Children Aboard

Ticket

Ticket Number

Fare

Passenger Fare

Cabin

Cabin

Embarked

Port of Embarkation

Source

https://www.kaggle.com/c/titanic/data
